    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It's honestly in pristine, showroom condition\u2014not a single scratch or dent anywhere! I've pampered this car since day one, and it still drives like an absolute dream. It basically looks and feels brand new inside and out. I'm sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 43500.0,
